  <answer><![CDATA[<p>Please contact your Travel Agent or call Reservations on <strong>01486 791111</strong> if you booked with us directly, as soon as possible to change any part of your holiday. We will then check if any charges apply from our suppliers and the availability of your new request. An admin fee of £25 per person may apply, as well as any additional costs from our suppliers. No significant changes can be made within 70 days of your departure.</p>
<p>If you booked online, please give us a call on <strong>01483 791111</strong> as changes need to be made over the phone.</p>]]></answer>
